           <a class="badge-tag m0" href="/help/badges/6091/zlib" title="gold badge: Earn at least 1000 total score for at least 200 non-community wiki answers in the zlib tag">
            <span class="badge1">
            </span>
            zlib
           </a>
          </div>
         </div>
         <div class="d-flex fl-grow1 ai-center md:w100">
          <div class="w24 fl-shrink0 d-none md:d-block">
          </div>
          <div class="flex--item fl-grow1">
           Earn at least 1000 total score for at least 200 non-community wiki answers in the
           <a class="post-tag" href="/questions/tagged/zlib" rel="tag" title="show questions tagged 'zlib'">
            zlib
           </a>
           tag
          </div>
          <div class="flex--item ml6 wmn1 md:wmn-initial ta-right fc-light fl-shrink0">
           <span title="1">
            1
           </span>
           awarded
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div>

     <div class="module" data-is-here-when="lg" id="badges-legend-module">
      <p class="mb24">
       These badges are awarded for participating in
       <b>
        non community-wiki questions
       </b>
       with particular tags. If enough votes are earned in a tag with 100+ total questions, the badge will be automatically created and awarded.
      </p>
      <div class="d-flex flex__fl-grow1 fd-column gs16 md:fd-row sm:fd-column">
       <div class="flex--item">
        <div>
         <a class="badge-tag" href="/help/badges?tab=tags&amp;filter=gold" title="gold badge: Earn at least 1000 total score for at least 200 non-community wiki answers in the Gold Tag Badge tag">
          <span class="badge1">
          </span>
          Gold Tag Badge
         </a>
        </div>
        <div>
         You must have a total score of 1000 in at least 200 non-community wiki answers to achieve this badge.
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="flex--item">
        <div>
         <a class="badge-tag" href="/help/badges?tab=tags&amp;filter=silver" title="silver badge: Earn at least 400 total score for at least 80 non-community wiki answers in the Silver Tag Badge tag">
          <span class="badge2">
          </span>
          Silver Tag Badge
         </a>
        </div>
        <div>
         You must have a total score of 400 in at least 80 non-community wiki answers to achieve this badge.
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="flex--item">
        <div>
         <a class="badge-tag" href="/help/badges?tab=tags&amp;filter=bronze" title="bronze badge: Earn at least 100 total score for at least 20 non-community wiki answers in the Bronze Tag Badge tag">
          <span class="badge3">
          </span>
          Bronze Tag Badge
         </a>
        </div>
        <div>
         You must have a total score of 100 in at least 20 non-community wiki answers to achieve this badge.
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
